title: Gold rankd
body: Earned gold rewards as gold 5 but never obtained maoki victorious just the maoki champion as i did not have him before was it a bug?

replies.body: Yeah, we're super close with giving out the rewards to eligible players.  A lot of players have received their goodies but might still be missing the victorious skin.  Don't worry, it's coming and on the way!  Hang tight until then!
Same thing happened to me, except whenever I check to see which skins I own for Maokai, the Victorious skin is listed as "Unavailable".
yes for me also listed as Unavailable.
